{
  "stem": "521.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I use the expression Russians because that's what we were using at that time, even though it was the Soviet Union which one contained Tajikistan, and Krygis, and all sorts of the other Tartars.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we just referred to them as the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were doing a very proper job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was done well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when the-- when the spring came, the ground melted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the hole-- hole in the ground was full of water and our beautiful work went up in smoke because the-- these tree trunks were swimming on top of the water.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't really do much for the water fjord of the German-Hungarian armies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After we were there for about, I would say, about two months or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And towards the end of March, we were-- they had decided that our group is going to go over to Poland and have the Hungarians in their water fjord.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As we were going up to mountain, they were-- the Hungarians were fighting the Russians with horse-drawn carts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- there were two horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the cart was full of ammunition or whatnot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were not motorized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were horse-drawn carts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, since these roads were very steep at certain places, we were told that we have to go, two of us, to each and every cart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were supposed to push and have the horses up the mountain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't wonder that the Hungarians and the Germans lost the war, because with this equipment, you don't really go very far.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that-- this time, the Russians were very close to the Polish-Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were past Kiev.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were very close to Stanislau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stanislau is the-- is the place where we were heading.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
